                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> Multiple creatures remain in area <strong>C4</strong> for more than 6 seconds.</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The whispers become more insistent until each character in the room must attempt a <span data-pf2-check=\"will\" data-pf2-traits=\"auditory,divine,emotion,enchantment,mental\" data-pf2-label=\"Luring Whispers DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"21\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Will</span> save.</p>\n<p>On a failure, a creature is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Confused]{Confused} for 1 round (or for [[/br 1d4+2 #rounds]] rounds on a critical failure). Both the audible whispers and the babbling of the confused are related to the haunting's origin.</p>\n<table class=\"pf2-table\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Owners</th>\n<th>Whispers and Babbles</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Archdevil worshippers</td>\n<td>Desperate praise of Mephistopheles</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Soulbound dollmakers</td>\n<td>Pleading \"don't make me go in the doll again\"</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Alchemical experimenters</td>\n<td>Frantic claims of not wanting to live forever anymore</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Slavers</td>\n<td>Begging to be allowed to be released in multiple languages</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Crime lords</td>\n<td>Promising not to mess with the family again</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Misguided Pharasmins</td>\n<td>Sighing desires to be put to rest</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>"
